\v 2 achiti: Tendeukai imwi; nokuti ushe hwokudenga hwava pedo.
\v 3 Nokuti uyu ndiye wakarehwa nezvake naIsaya muporofita, achiti: Inzwi rounodana murenje: Gadzirirai mugwagwa waShe, ruramisai nzira yake.
\v 4 Iyezve Johwani waiva nenguvo yake yamambava ekamera nebhanhire redehwe pachiuno chake; nezvokudya zvake zvaiva mhashu nouchi hwedondo.
\v 5 Zvino kwakabudira kwaari Jerusarema neJudhiya rose nedunhu rose rakapoteredza Jorodhani;
>>>>>>> 446d919009b5b36ef27b0b3f8c6dc928fc44c133:Matthew/3/data
\v 6 vakabhabhatidzwa naye muna Joridhani vachireurura zvivi zvavo.
\p
\v 7 Asi wakati achiona vazhinji vavaFarisi navaSadhusi vachiuya kurubhabhatidzo rwake, akati kwavari: Zvizvarwa zvenyoka, ndianiko wakakutendekerai kuti mutize hasha dzinouya?
\v 8 Naizvozvo berekai zvibereko zvakafanira kutendeuka.
\v 9 Musafunga kutaura mukati menyu \add muchiti\add*: Tina Abhurahamu baba, nokuti ndinoti kwamuri: Mwari unokwanisa kubva pamabwe awa kumutsira Abhurahamu vana.
\v 10 Ikozvino sanhuwo ratoiswa pamudzi yemiti, naizvozvo muti mumwe nomumwe usingabereki zvibereko zvakanaka unotemwa ugokandirwa mumoto.
\v 11 Ini zvirokwazvo ndinokubhabhatidzai nemvura mupinde mukutendeuka, asi uyo unouya shure kwangu unesimba kupfuureni, neshangu dzake handina kufanira kudzitakura, Iye uchakubhabhatidzai noMweya Mutsvene nomoto.
\v 12 Rusero rwake \add ruri\add* muruvoko rwake, uchatsvaira buriro rake kwazvo, agounganidzira zviyo mudura, asi hundi ucha\add i\add*pisa nemoto usingadzimwi.
\s Kubhabhatidzwa kwaJesu
\p
\v 13 Zvino Jesu wakabva Garirea akasvika paJoridhani kuna Johwani, kuzobhabhatidzwa naye.
\v 14 Asi Johwani wakamudzivisa achiti: Ndini ndinofanira kubhabhatidzwa nemwi, asi mouya kwandiri \add sei\add*?
\v 15 Asi Jesu achipindura wakati kwaari: Tenda hako zvino nokuti saizvozvo zvakafanira kuti tizadzise kururama kose. Ipapo akamutendera.
\v 16 Asi Jesu, wakati abhabhatidzwa, akabuda pakarepo mumvura: Zvino tarira, kudenga kwakamuzarurirwa, akaona Mweya waMwari achiburuka senjiva, achiuya pamusoro pake.
\v 17 Zvino tarira inzwi rakabva kudenga richiti: Uyu ndiye Mwanakomana wangu unodika, wandinofara maari kwazvo!
